{"tid":2311800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃毓民聲援許智峯和「眾志三子」","createTime":"2020-12-04T10:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T19:01:57.000Z","uid":134071,"like":277,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"064cb2b65b78d08f32b1e865cbd2635df216a553","tid":2311800,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"佢係節目仲有對人抽水&nbsp;(屌民主黨,&nbsp;屌熱血公民),&nbsp;但佢今次聲援許智峯和「眾志三子」,&nbsp;點都係好事.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np1 of 4<br />\n香港沒有免於恐懼的自由 許智峯將婦挈雛流亡海外<br />\n<a href=\"https://myradio.hk/?p=99813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyradio.hk%2F%3Fp%3D99813&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=1a3294e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myradio.hk/?p=99813</a><br />\np2 of 4<br />\n鼠王芬舐共無下限踩多一腳 指許言行涉觸犯港區國安法<br />\n<a href=\"https://myradio.hk/?p=99812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyradio.hk%2F%3Fp%3D99812&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=956abbf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myradio.hk/?p=99812</a><br />\np3 of 4<br />\n重判黃之鋒周庭林朗彥只會加強政治抗爭運動的道德基礎<br />\n<a href=\"https://myradio.hk/?p=99811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyradio.hk%2F%3Fp%3D99811&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=dff3cc83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myradio.hk/?p=99811</a><br />\np4 of 4<br />\n「眾志三子」已經成為海内外認可的香港反抗運動領袖<br />\n<a href=\"https://myradio.hk/?p=99810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyradio.hk%2F%3Fp%3D99810&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=50abe390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myradio.hk/?p=99810</a>"},{"pid":"dd38b197f7a2a214c34f76fbaf043121cbf5cb49","tid":2311800,"uid":134071,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"反而,&nbsp;連登有一位分化撚,&nbsp;自稱毓民信徙.<br />\n但佢係呢兩日仲狂串許智峯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal